title: Roswell - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 6/1/22
itunes:title: Roswell - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 6/1/22
description:
George Noory and author Don Schmitt explore the famous UFO crash in Roswell New Mexico, his interviews with witnesses who saw debris from the crashed flying saucer, and why the government has continued to cover up evidence of the crash for nearly 75 years.
